snippet.title: AARGH! the Pirate in... Shark Attack Smackdown! (2007) - Full Playthrough
snippet.description:
Full playthrough of AARGH! the Pirate, an online game originally published on Zeeks and Funschool.
This playthrough was recorded on Christmas Day, and I wish you all a Merry Christmas!

This game is basically a re-skin of another Zeeks/Funschool game called Whomp. Wallop and Whack-o-Wheen are also re-skins of the same game.

#playthrough #nostalgia #flashgames
